title: #92Noon! Evason/Moss/Russo/Motzko/Entz/Miles/Finch
description: Busy show! Wild coach Dean Evason celebrates another win to start the show, then NCAA Tourney handicapping with VSIN's Mitch Moss and Russo Radio ends the first hour...Midway thru, hear Gopher hockey coach Bob Motzko on the Big 10 title victory...final hour features NDSU football coach Matt Entz, former hoops coach-turned-analyst(but wants to coach again) Tim Miles, and Wolves coach Chris Finch to finish the show!
